Rail industry information services. Umler equipment registry, RailSight visibility, eCommerce messaging, JTOS (Joint Terminal Operations System), RailConnect. Standardized rail data and communications.
Railinc's TMS platform for shippers. Rail shipment management, visibility, reporting. Integrates with Railinc data services.
Transportation management software for 3PLs and shippers. Planning, execution, settlement. Multi-modal capabilities.

Freight tracking and visibility platform. Real-time load tracking across all modes. Integrates with TMS for enhanced visibility.
Technology-driven freight brokerage with TMS. Intermodal rail services, truckload, LTL, supply chain management.

TMS with rail intermodal integration. Partnership with CSX RailPlus for door-to-door intermodal service. Rate optimization, tracking, demurrage, audit, pay for rail. Multi-modal visibility platform.

Transportation management system now part of BluJay. Planning, execution, settlement. Multi-modal including rail.

Transportation management services and technology. Intermodal rail, truckload, LTL, managed transportation.
Transportation management for trucking, 3PLs, private fleets. Dispatch, fleet maintenance, accounting.
